ls which may include senior, junior, novice, and below.<ref>[http://www.moksz.hu/external/mukorcsolya/2017_2018/halloween_cup/nonISU/ ''International Halloween Cup 2017'' Non-ISU results]</ref><ref>[http://www.moksz.hu/external/mukorcsolya/2018_2019/Halloween_Cup/result/NonISU/index.htm ''International Halloween Cup 2018'' Non-ISU results]</ref><ref>[http://hunskate.hu/external/mukorcsolya/2019_2020/Halloween/eredmenyek/NONISU/index.htm ''International Halloween Cup 2019'' Non-ISU results]</ref>\n\n== Senior medalists ==\n=== Men ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! colspan=5 align=\"center\" | Senior men\n|-\n! Year\n| align=center bgcolor=gold | '''Gold'''\n| align=center bgcolor=silver | '''Silver'''\n| align=center bgcolor=cc9966 | '''Bronze'''\n! Details\n|-\n| 2018 || {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Brendan Kerry]] || {{flagicon|GBR}} [[Graham Newberry]] || {{flagicon|HUN}} [[Alexander Maszljanko]] || <ref>[http://www.moksz.hu/external/mukorcsolya/2018_2019/Halloween_Cup/result/ISU/CAT010RS.HTM Senior men results 2018]</ref>\n|-\n| 2019 || {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Brendan Kerry]] || {{flagicon|UKR}} [[Ivan Shmuratko]] || {{flagicon|TUR}} [[Burak Demirboga]] || <ref>[http://hunskate.hu/external/mukorcsolya/2019_2020/Halloween/eredmenyek/ISU/CAT012RS.HTM Senior men results 2019]</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n=== Ladies ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! colspan=5 align=\"center\" | Senior ladies\n|-\n! Year\n| align=center bgcolor=gold | '''Gold'''\n| align=center bgcolor=silver | '''Silver'''\n| align=center bgcolor=cc9966 | '''Bronze'''\n! Details\n|-\n| 2018 || {{flagicon|SUI}} [[Alexia Paganini]] || {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Anita \u00d6stlund]] || {{flagicon|HUN}} [[Ivett T\u00f3th]] || <ref>[http://www.moksz.hu/external/mukorcsolya/2018_2019/Halloween_Cup/result/ISU/CAT011RS.HTM Senior ladies results 2018]</ref>\n|-\n| 2019 || {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Lucrezia Beccari]] || {{flagicon|HUN}} [[J\u00falia L\u00e1ng]] || {{flagicon|FIN}} [[Linnea Ceder]] || <ref>[http://hunskate.hu/external/mukorcsolya/2019_2020/H