BC\n| {{start date|2020|03|29}}\n| TBC\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n[[Category:2015 podcast debuts]]\n[[Category:Audio podcasts]]\n[[Category:Comedy and humor podcasts]]\n[[Category:Film and television podcasts]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use mdy dates|date=January 2020}}\n{{short description|American podcast}}\n{{Infobox podcast\n|title        = Blank Check with Griffin & David\n|image        = [[File:Blank check podcast logo.jpg|250px]]\n|caption      =\n|host         = {{Unbulleted list\n|[[Griffin Newman]] \n|David Sims\n}}\n|language     = English\n|website      = [https://audioboom.com/channel/Blank-Check Blank Check]\n|updates      = Weekly\n|production   = Ben Hosley\n|audio format = Podcast (via streaming or downloadable MP3)\n|began        = {{Start date|2015|3|23}}\n|ended        =\n|num_seasons =\n|num_episodes =\n|runtime = Variable (2-3 hours)\n|genre        = Film\n|cited_for    = \n|cited_as     = \n|provider     = [[AudioBoom]]\n}}\n'''''Blank Check with Griffin & David''''' is a film podcast following the career output of directors who have had significant success and are then offered a figurative ''blank check'' to pursue their passion projects. Most episodes focus on a single movie from the director's filmography.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://audioboom.com/channel/Blank-Check |access-date=August 28, 2019 |title=Blank Check with Griffin & David}}</ref> The show is hosted by ''[[The Atlantic]]'' film critic David Sims and actor [[Griffin Newman]].\n\n''Blank Check'' has been positively reviewed by ''[[Paste Magazine]]'',<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2018/07/blank-check-and-the-intersection-of-comedy-and-cri.html |title=Blank Check and the Intersection of Comedy and Criticism |last=Techler |first=Graham |work=Paste Magazine | date=July 5, 2018 |access-date=August 28, 2019}}</ref> ''[[Decider (website)|Decider]]'',<ref name=\"decider\">{{cite news|url=https://decider.com/2016/01/28/blank-check-is-the-movie-podcast-y