 Rain Games\n| Playdigious\n| [[Metroidvania]]\n| {{dts|2018|11|08}}\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Tetris (Electronic Arts)|Tetris]]''\n| [[EA Mobile]]\n| [[Electronic Arts]]\n| [[Puzzle video game|Puzzle]]\n| {{dts|2011|09|01}}\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Tetris Blitz]]''\n| [[Electronic Arts]]\n| Electronic Arts\n| [[Puzzle video game|Puzzle]]\n| {{dts|2013|05|17}}\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Tiny Troopers]]''\n| Kukouri Mobile Entertainment\n| Chillingo\n| [[Action game|Action]]\n| {{dts|2012|06|07}}\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Unkilled]]''\n| [[Madfinger Games]]\n| Madfinger Games\n| [[First-person shooter]]\n| {{dts|2015|09|03}}\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Vainglory (video game)|Vainglory]]''\n| [[Super Evil Megacorp]]\n| Super Evil Megacorp\n| [[Multiplayer online battle arena]]\n| {{dts|2015|07|02}}\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Vikings: War of Clans]]''\n| Kooapps\n| Kooapps\n| [[Massively multiplayer online]], [[Strategy video game|strategy]]\n| {{dts|2015|08|10}}\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Voez]]''\n| Rayark Games\n| Rayark Games\n| [[Rhythm game|Rhythm]]\n| {{dts|2016|06|02}}\n|\n|-\n| ''[[VVVVVV]]''\n| [[Terry Cavanagh (developer)|Terry Cavanagh]]\n| Terry Cavanagh\n| [[Platform video game|2D platformer]], [[metroidvania]]\n| {{dts|2014|06|12}}\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Walking Dead: Road to Survival]]''\n| IUGO Mobile Entertainment\n| [[Scopely]]\n| [[Action role-playing]]\n| {{dts|2015|08|27}}\n|\n|-\n| ''[[XCOM: Enemy Within]]''\n| [[Firaxis Games]]\n| [[2K Games]]\n| [[Strategy video game|Strategy]]\n| {{dts|2014|11|13}}\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Yo-kai Watch: Wibble Wobble]]''\n| [[Level-5 (company)|Level-5]]\n| Level-5\n| [[Puzzle video game|Puzzle]], [[Role-playing video game|role-playing]]\n| {{vgrelease|JP|October 21, 2015|NA|March 24, 2016|EU|March 30, 2017}}\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Links]]''\n| [[Konami]]\n| Konami\n| [[Card game]]\n| {{vgrelease|JP|November 17, 2016|WW|January 11, 2017}}\n|\n|}\n\n==Notes==\n{{notelist}}\n\n{{Video game lists by platform}}\n{{Android}}\n\n[[Category:Android (operating system) games| ]]\n[[Category:Lists of mobile apps]]